Russell King Sr. went to all of the court hearings involving Lane. He is survived by his wife, Jeannie, and their older daughter, Crystal.

A year ago, families of the three slain students filed a wrongful-death lawsuit against the teenage gunman and his family. The suit alleged negligent supervision by Lane's parents and grandparents.

